          </p>

          <h2>Copyright</h2>
          <p>
            All text, images, video and design elements on this site are protected by copyright. Reproduction, distribution or any other use beyond the limits of copyright law requires the prior written consent of Skydive Luxembourg a.s.b.l. or the respective rights holder.
          </p>
        </>
